<HEADLINE>  Bosnia Serb Premier Eases Stance </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	BANJA LUKA, Bosnia-Herzegovina (AP) -- Signaling an easing of  
tensions, the premier of Bosnia's Serbs today softened his threat 
to resign following an international ruling that removed a 
